text: The 2019–20 GKK Šibenka season is the 10th season in the existence of the club. The club played in the Croatian League. ==Overview== On 13 June 2019, club's main sponsor Doğuş Group reported they will leave the club after 7 years as the main sponsor. On 27 June 2019, it was established a new board and owner led by the president Ante Burić.
